<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Raven</title>
  <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <![endif]-->
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
  <p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
</head>
<body>
   <div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
    <div class="navbar-inner">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".nav-collapse">
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        </a>
        <a class="brand" href="#">Raven Store</a>
        <div class="nav-collapse">
          <ul class="nav">
            <li><%= link_to "Browse Songs", songs_path %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "About Raven", pages_about_path %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Contact Us", pages_about_path  %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Home", pages_home_path %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="usernav">
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        Signed in as <%= current_user.email %>
        <%= link_to "Sign Out", destroy_user_session_path, :method => :delete %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path %> or <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <ul class="hmenu">
    <%= render 'devise/menu/registration_items' %>
    <%= render 'devise/menu/login_items' %>
  </ul>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span9"> <%= yield %> </div>
      <div class="span3">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse lacinia tempor scelerisque. Fusce a nulla interdum quam adipiscing ultrices. Donec nulla massa, tincidunt malesuada facilisis nec, facilisis sit amet magna. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Nullam laoreet nunc in justo ornare sed hendrerit mi mollis. Phasellus a sem metus, sit amet iaculis urna. Cras sollicitudin vehicula ipsum, ac tincidunt eros consectetur et. Morbi a elit in odio semper imperdiet eget ac leo.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
